HTML-Controls

A library of controls/widgets to use in HTML forms to separate
'external' (i.e. in the HTML) representation from 'internal' (i.e. in
the program) representation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


